      <td width="692"><div style="text-align: center;">
      </div><h2 align="justify"><small><font face="Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif">WHAT ARE WE?</font></small></h2>
      <p style="text-align: left;"><font face="Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif">A day school, one of the
few in the United States, dedicated to teaching students the ancient
and honorable art of the clown. We are committed to the idea of a clown
understood a</font><font face="Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif">s an actor versed in the skills of physical comedy.</font></p><h2 align="justify"><font><font face="Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif"><img style="border: 1px solid ; width: 160px; height: 241px; float: right;" alt="Mike_Salvino" src="px/morph/mike2flapjack.gif" hspace="5"></font></font><small><font face="Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif">HOW?</font></small></h2>
      
      <p style="text-align: left;"><font face="Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif">Through our </font><font face="Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif">thirty weeks </font><font face="Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif">course of
instruction we focus on character
development, physical skills and performing techniques.</font></p>
      <h2 align="justify"><small><font face="Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif">WHO DO WE SERVE?</font></small></h2>
      <p style="text-align: left;"><font face="Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif">Whoever seeks the way of
the clown. We accept those who have no clowning or performing
experience as well as those who wish to develop or refine their
performing abilities.</font></p>
      <h2 align="justify"><small><font face="Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif">HOW MUCH DO WE COST?</font></small></h2>
      <p style="text-align: left;"><font face="Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif">Our course of
instruction is constantly developing. Costs range $1295 &#8211; $1495 plus supplies for our course of instruction. After a
consultation, we are able to be more specific concerning individual
student expenses.</font></p>
      <h2 align="justify"><small><font face="Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif">WHERE ARE WE?</font></small></h2>
      <p style="text-align: left;"><font face="Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif">We are located in Akron,
Ohio, USA. We do travel nationally and internationally. Please consult
our &#8220;<a href="http://www.ohiocollegeclowningarts.com/road.html" target="_blank">On the Road</a>&#8221; page for information concerning that
program.</font></p>
      <p align="justify"><big><span style="font-family: Georgia,Times New Roman,Times,serif; font-weight: bold;">NON-DESCRIMINATION
STATEMENT</span></big></p>
      <font face="Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif">The
Ohio College of Clowning Arts complies with all federal and state rules
and does not discriminate on the basis of race, color, national origin,
gender or disability.&nbsp; This holds true for all students and/or
faculty
who are interested in participating in educational programs or
extracurricular activities of the college.</font>
